In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Diane Serafin BLANK. No. D-2746. Supreme Court of the United States Nov. 12, 2013.

Diane Serafin Blank, of New York, New York, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring her to show cause why she should not disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
